          "entries": [
            {
              "title": "About the Course",
              "content": "Develop hand-eye coordination while playing with words and rhythm using ball-bouncing, passing, and clapping games.\n\nThis topic is included in the following course(s): PE: Grades 1-3\n\nPE: Grades 1-3\nLessons specifically created for Grades 1-6. We recommend you make sure to include some sort of physical activity as breaks throughout your school day. If you already have sports or similar activities as a regular part of your life rhythms, these lessons are optional."
            }
          ]
